                <p class="card-text">During my education and solo work, all of the projects I have been working on are available on my Github, with most being public to be downloaded or branched.</p>
                <a href="https://github.com/mriley-wallace" class="btn btn-primary">Take a look at my repo</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <br />
        <br />

        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header">
                Itch.IO Page
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">

                <h5 class="card-title">All of my released games are on Itch.IO</h5>
